### Create a new project 
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
    "name": "Project now",
    "description": "Description now",
    "endDate": "2025-07-31T23:59:59Z"
